The paper analyzes and predicts closed questions on Stack Overflow, which involves machine learning and textual analysis. This suggests that it could fall under the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
